(222, 1, '2018-04-06 11:56:23', '2018-04-06 11:56:23', 'Officially opened on Thursday 5th April, by a ribbon cutting ceremony, the event was officiated by Professor Greg Hill, Vice-Chancellor and President of USC, the Hon Victor Dominello, MP, NSW Minister for Finance, Services and Property, Dr Manish Malhotra, Founder and CEO of ATMC, Mr. Puneet Gupta, CIO of ATMC, Lynne Clements, Dir of Campus Operations, ATMC, Professor Mike Clements, Chief Academic Officer of ATMC also Prof Graham Bowery & John Ridge were presented there at this historic moment.We put great emphasis on employability and meaningful outcomes for our students and that reflects well on the universities that we partner with. “In practical terms, this means that international students take home more than just degrees. They also take home an understanding of Australian culture, communication styles and an insight into how we do business.”The focus on student retention, smaller classes, and services to improve student well-being mean ATMC campuses are a much more welcoming environment for international students. ATMC campuses allow students to gain a better understanding of Australian culture and society, and they go beyond teaching to foster long-term relationships and create a global community,” Dr Manish Malhotra said.A total of 592 students and faculty staff will attend the Kent Street Campus, which will be a dedicated USC campus catering specifically to international students.\r\nThe new Kent Street campus is a designed specifically to improve the experience of international students.\r\nThe new campus will focus on the delivery of business courses including undergraduate and postgraduate degrees.\r\n\r\nMore details here: http://dailybulletin.com.au/news/37435-australia-s-newest-higher-education-facility-opens-in-the-centre-of-sydney\r\n\r\n', 'ATMC & USC jointly put the foundation stone for a New Campus in the Heart of Sydney, Australia.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'school-fair-event', '', '', '2018-09-23 23:30:25', '2018-09-23 23:30:25', '', 0, 'http://raratheme.com/preview/education-zone-pro/?post_type=event&#038;p=222', 0, 'event', '', 0),
