(231, 1, '2016-12-30 05:12:26', '2016-12-30 05:12:26', 'Studying in college is a lot different than in high school. I study by reading a lot more than I ever have and I listen in class to make sure I remember what\'s been talked about in the lectures. I also type out study guides for all of my classes, which I don\'t think I ever did in high school until it got to final exam time.', 'Aaron Ford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aaron-ford', '', '', '2016-12-30 05:12:26', '2016-12-30 05:12:26', '', 0, 'http://raratheme.com/preview/education-zone-pro/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=231', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
