(659, 1, '2018-09-23 23:21:04', '2018-09-23 23:21:04', 'Officially opened on Thursday 5th April, by a ribbon cutting ceremony, the event was officiated by Professor Greg Hill, Vice-Chancellor and President of USC, the Hon Victor Dominello, MP, NSW Minister for Finance, Services and Property, Dr Manish Malhotra, Founder and CEO of ATMC, Mr. Puneet Gupta, CIO of ATMC, Lynne Clements, Dir of Campus Operations, ATMC, Professor Mike Clements, Chief Academic Officer of ATMC also Prof Graham Bowery & John Ridge were presented there at this historic moment.We put great emphasis on employability and meaningful outcomes for our students and that reflects well on the universities that we partner with. “In practical terms, this means that international students take home more than just degrees. They also take home an understanding of Australian culture, communication styles and an insight into how we do business.”', 'ATMC & USC jointly put the foundation stone for a New Campus in the Heart of Sydney, Australia.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '222-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-09-23 23:21:04', '2018-09-23 23:21:04', '', 222, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2018/09/23/222-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
