(690, 1, '2018-09-24 00:14:50', '2018-09-24 00:14:50', 'Our college ATMC provides the courses offered by three universities: University of Sunshine coast, Federation University Australia and Charles Darwin University. All the universities offered the courses called industrial project. Every semester, students make different projects in different fields like pHp, Java, .net, Networking, Android, etc. \r\nATMC administration realize that they need a software or website which is used to represents these projects made by their students to the public. Administration wants to show the talent of their students to the world. So, they assign us this project named “ATMC SHOWCASE”. This is a project that will used to display the projects like an exhibition-software.\r\n\r\n', 'ATMC SHOWCASE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '172-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-24 00:14:50', '2018-09-24 00:14:50', '', 172, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2018/09/24/172-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
